---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="How to Choose the Right Plant Extract Supplier in 2024 | Weiyijie Bio"
  description="Complete guide to choosing a reliable plant extract supplier. Learn the key factors to consider: certifications, quality control, MOQ, pricing, delivery time, and after-sales service."
>
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem)] font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">How to Choose the Right Plant Extract Supplier in 2024</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">A complete buying guide for manufacturers, brands, and distributors looking for high-quality plant extract suppliers.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">1. Verify Certifications First</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">The first and most important factor to check is whether the supplier can provide the necessary certifications for your market:
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-3 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>US market:</strong> FDA registration, cGMP compliance, Kosher/Halal if required</li>
            <li><strong>EU market:</strong> REACH registration, EC number, EINECS number, GMP certification</li>
            <li><strong>Global markets:</strong> ISO 9001 quality management system certification</li>
          </ul>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Always ask for copies of certifications before placing an order, and verify their validity if possible.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">2. Evaluate Quality Control System</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">A reliable supplier should have a strict quality control process throughout the entire production chain:
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-3 space-y-2">
            <li>Raw material inspection before entering production</li>
            <li>In-process quality monitoring during extraction and purification</li>
            <li>Comprehensive finished product testing before shipment</li>
            <li>Sample retention system for traceability (at least 2 years)</li>
            <li>Third-party testing reports available upon request</li>
          </ul>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Always request a free sample first to test the quality before placing a bulk order.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">3. Check Production Capacity and MOQ</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Make sure the supplier can meet your order volume requirements, both small and large:
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-3 space-y-2">
            <li>Minimum Order Quantity (MOQ): Look for suppliers that offer small MOQs (1kg or lower) for testing purposes</li>
            <li>Maximum production capacity: Ensure they can handle your bulk orders when your business scales</li>
            <li>Lead time: Typical lead time for regular orders should be 3-7 days for stock items, 15-30 days for custom production</li>
          </ul>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">4. Consider Pricing and Payment Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">While price is important, it should not be the only deciding factor:
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-3 space-y-2">
            <li>Compare prices from multiple suppliers, but be wary of prices that are significantly lower than market average (usually indicates poor quality)</li>
            <li>Look for transparent pricing with no hidden fees</li>
            <li>Flexible payment terms: T/T, PayPal, Alibaba Trade Assurance for new customers</li>
            <li>Discounts for bulk orders and long-term cooperation</li>
          </ul>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">5. Evaluate Customer Service and Support</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Good after-sales service can save you a lot of trouble:
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-3 space-y-2">
            <li>Fast response time: Look for suppliers that reply to inquiries within 24 hours</li>
            <li>Technical support: Can they provide formulation advice and technical guidance?</li>
            <li>After-sales policy: What happens if the product quality does not meet standards?</li>
            <li>Clear communication: English-speaking sales team for international customers</li>
          </ul>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-green-200">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-800 mb-4">Why Choose Weiyijie Bio as Your Plant Extract Supplier?</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Full certifications:</strong> FDA/REACH/GMP/Kosher/Halal/ISO 9001 certified, all documents available</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Strict quality control:</strong> 4-step quality inspection process, COA provided for every batch</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Flexible MOQ:</strong> 1kg MOQ for most products, perfect for testing and small businesses</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Fast delivery:</strong> 3-5 days for stock items, 7-15 days global shipping</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>24/7 support:</strong> English-speaking sales team, reply within 24 hours</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-6 text-center">
          <a href="/#contact" class="bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg inline-block transition-all">
            Request Free Quote / Sample
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
